                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1955.1.2728/view">BZS.1955.1.2728</ref>,
                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1951.31.5.1955/view">BZS.1951.31.5.1955</ref>,
                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1958.106.3049/view">BZS.1958.106.3049</ref>,
                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1958.106.5568/view">BZS.1958.106.5568</ref>,
                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1958.106.2219/view">BZS.1958.106.2219</ref>,
                      <ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1955.1.3272/view">BZS.1955.1.3272</ref>).
                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-6">
                      [6]. <bibl><ptr target="Seibt1976"/>, <citedRange unit="part">22</citedRange></bibl>; <bibl><ptr target="DOseals3"/>, <citedRange unit="part"><ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1955.1.3270/view">86.25</ref></citedRange></bibl>, 
