                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-7">
                      [7]. <bibl><ptr target="Cheynet1985"/>, <citedRange unit="page">p. 188</citedRange></bibl>.
                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-8">
                      [8]. Κύριε βοήθει Λέοντι μαγίστρῳ βέστῃ καὶ στρατηγῷ τῶν Βουκελλαρίων τῷ Ἰασίτῃ:
                      <bibl><ptr target="DOseals4"/>, <citedRange unit="part"><ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1955.1.3062/view">1.32</ref></citedRange></bibl>. Pour sa carrière, <bibl><ptr target="BBÖ1"/>, <citedRange unit="part">40</citedRange></bibl>. Le premier duc connu, Michel Maurix,
                      était proèdre: <bibl><ptr target="DOseals4"/>, <citedRange unit="part"><ref target="https://www.doaks.org/resources/seals/byzantine-seals/BZS.1958.106.2995/view">1.6</ref></citedRange></bibl>;
